cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about reinforcement learning algorithms, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on exploration and exploitation suggests that the paper may also be relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the use of high-dimensional control tasks in MuJoCo simulator suggests that computer vision (cs.CV) may also be relevant.
